<div class="prod-desc" itemprop="description">
	<p class="p1">I love this Room Spray so much because it doesn&#8217;t just fill a room with fragrance—it creates an ambience.</p>
<p>Complement the Room Spray with our beautiful, hand-poured <span style="color: #cc99ff;"><a style="color: #cc99ff;" href="http://www.mrspotter.com/product/winter-soy-glass-candle/" target="_blank">Soy Glass Candle.</a></span></p>
<p><strong>Lilac<br />
</strong>Invite the sweet scents of fresh-cut Lilac blooms into your home with my delicately fragrant Lilac Room Spray.</p>
<p><strong>Clover<br />
</strong>Welcome Spring a little early this year with our fresh new Clover Room Spray, sweet with notes of newly cut grass, morning dew, and blooming wisteria.</p>
<p><strong>Crimson<br />
</strong>Fill your home with the elegant bouquet of star jasmine and white lily scents paired with rich Indonesian patchouli and warm notes of cinnamon, creamy French vanilla, and sensual white musk.</p>
<p>&nbsp;</p>
<p><em><em><strong> </strong></em></em></p>
<p>Due to the hand-crafted nature of all our products, we offer each item in limited quantities.</p>
<p><em>Questions or concerns about your order? Contact us at <a style="color: #cc99ff;" href="mailto:support@mrspotter.com">support@mrspotter.com</a> and we&#8217;ll get back to you within 24 hours. </em></p>
</div><div class="product_meta">

	
	
